CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper March 29, 1958, pg. 6, reads: "11 Taverns in Five Blocks - Six of the 11 liquor dispensing establishments between Brushton and Lang Aves., on Frankstown Ave., a five-block area are, (top left picture): The Crystal Bar in the 7600 block... - All Photos by Harris."
TitMainTitle: 7600 block of Frankstown Avenue with Crystal Bar, mail truck, and 87 Ardmore streetcar in background, Homewood
